description: Everything you need to know about coronavirus, including the latest news, how it is impacting our lives, and how to prepare and protect yourself.
title: The Covid-19 Pandemic
title_page: The Covid-19 Pandemic - The New York Times
maintext: After over two years of living with Covid-19, we are learning to adapt to a world with this disease. In the first two years of the pandemic, nearly 15 million more people died globally than would have been expected during normal times, and over one million Americans have died.
